snippet.title: Dark Hours - Players' React Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2208570

Dark Hours is a co-op survival horror game for 1-4 players. Your heist has been disrupted by a supernatural event, and your team of robbers is now trapped with an evil entity. Forget your plan, your mission now is to survive. Explore and cooperate to find a way out or try to hide until morning.

Special Thanks to our content creators for their screams and laughter: 
- @ardashe 
- @box94vods57 
- @daukey

- @Orbital_Inc
